Text: Yes... That's good progress.
I think...time to sleep...a little—

Oh, Eta! Don't tell me you stayed up all night
again?!

I did... I finished everything, so today's the
last time.

I should hope so! You haven't slept in four days,
your skin's going to be a mess!
Shall I make...medicine for that?
What? That's actually a pretty good―

No, wait! Any really handy drug like that is bound
to have some terrible side effects.
Darn...
Wait... Were you trying to use me as a guinea pig?!
Of course. You're always so careful...with your skin.

Grrr... Well, I mean, skin is so important, and I
suppose if we could work out the timing...

...Anyway, you want something? I...want to sleep...
already—
Oh, that's right! I'm here to get you cleaned up.
But... I'm going to bed.
But, still!
Why?

You've been locked up in your lab all this time, so
you might not have noticed, or even care, but...

The Shadow Garden is busier than it's ever been
before.
Busier than...when Gamma started...Mitsugoshi...?
Yes. And this time we're preparing for battle.

Right, so that's why...Lady Alpha asked me for
something.
Is that right?

Yes. She's oddly excited... She said, it's okay to
make something...really crazy.
Excited? In a good way?
Yes. Very excited.

That's almost scary to imagine. But, I am prepared
for this.
I see... Well, then...good night—
Hold on, we're not done talking!
Oh...can't it wait until later—
We're not done yet!
You didn't come here...to talk about that...?
No, I'm just getting started!

By cleaned up, I mean we need to get you ready for
the real battle.

It can't wait...for the day of the battle...? Am I
even going to...fight?

Of course you are! This battle will decide the
Garden's future!

You can't go into it looking unrested! You need to
look your best with shiny hair and everything.
...Do I need that? For...battle?
Well, no... But, here I am anyway!
Huhhh... You serious?
I am! Master Shadow never fights with mussed hair!

We are the Seven Shadows, lurking in the darkness
and hunting down shadows.

Joining in a major battle without following Master
Shadow's aesthetic is simply out of the question!
Oh, fine, I get it...

...I won't get in your way... Just do...what you
need...to do...
Right, right, as long as you understand.
Heehee, your hair really is gorgeous, Eta.

If you took proper care of it every single day, you'd
have the silkiest hair of the Seven Shadows.

Oh, but that would mean that I wouldn't have the best
hair anymore...

But I might not mind losing to this lovely
silkiness... No indeed!
Big battle...!
I see...I can...run some experiments... Hehe.
Did inspiration strike?
Yes... Epsilon, give me a hand...
I don't want to be a guinea pig!

This time, it'll be fine... The guinea pigs...won't
be your hands...but the enemy...!

That "this time" worries me, but... Oh well,
I suppose it'll be fine.
*yawn*... Can I sleep, like this?
Hold on, I'm still not done!
Zzzz...

Oh, Eta... Always going her own way, or just not
giving a damn...
Maybe I could learn something from that boldness...

In this next battle, I'm going to show off my
precision and beauty!
